items.Furniture_Forgotten_Nytha_Candle.name = Forgotten Nytha Candle
items.Furniture_Forgotten_Nytha_Candle.description = Oh, Forgotten Nytha. We know of you so. We weep for what you where. Thou hail from time immemorial, and bless only us few with knowledge of your purpose. You who gave us the secrets of life and death, why still did they look down upon you? Did you truly deserve the fate you were given? I mourn for all that could have been, as do we all. Oh, Forgotten Nytha. The tragedy of the Abyss rings true.

items.Spawner_Spectre.name = Spectre Anchor
items.Spawner_Spectre.description = A magic anchor to bind a spirit to the world, tethering them back to the point once everyday.

items.Bench_Forsaken_Altar.name = Forsaken Altar
items.Bench_Forsaken_Altar.description = An altar to the old kin. They are not satisfied until the end. Bring them more, they may grant you pity. Tithe thy lords, for Forgotten Nytha was not enough. They require more. Bring them the world, they will grant you your pittance.

